aimedAtTarget 
Game: ArmA 2: Operation Arrowhead (1.51) 
Description: Returns how good the weapon of the vehicle is aimed at the target 
.  
Syntax:  
 vehicle aimedAtTarget [target, weapon] 
Parameters: 
vehicle: Object 
[target, weapon]: Array 
target: Object 
weapon: String - (optional) 
Return Value: 
 Number